race.comment: DURAZZO (1) brings a near miss and a win in Listed grade to resumption. Spaced the rivals in a trial at Longford recently and looks ready to pick up where he left off. Tough to beat with average luck from an awkward gate. ALVARINHO (4) resumes and has placed at Listed and Group level. Goes on the fresh side and her figures stack right up. She's right up to this on song. AND BEYOND (2) resumes with the leading hoop booked. Maps for the run of the race and he's in the mix putting his best foot forward. FURNEAUX (8) finished fifth last start, beaten 3 lengths at Launceston over 1200m. Worth keeping safe.
